'''''Kaerlighed ved forste hik''''' (''Love at First Hiccough'') is a 1999 Danish drama film based on the novel by [[Dennis J<U+00FC>rgensen]].

== Cast ==
* [[Robert Hansen (actor)|Robert Hansen]] - Viktor
* [[Sofie Lassen-Kahlke]] - Anja
* [[Sebastian Jessen]] - Brian 
* [[Rasmus Albeck]] - Esben 
* Karl Bille - Thorkild
* Jonas G<U+00FC>lstorff - Nikolaj
* Joachim Knop - Peter


